== Playoff seeds ==
After the regular season, the standard of 16 teams qualified for the playoffs. The [[San Jose Sharks]] were the [[Western Conference (NHL)|Western Conference]] regular season champions and the [[Presidents' Trophy]] winners with the best record at 117 points. The [[Boston Bruins]] earned a number 1 seed in the [[Eastern Conference (NHL)|Eastern Conference]] with 116 points.

